### Trigger a test transaction
POST https://us-central1-thinktwice-kamihack.cloudfunctions.net/api/webhook/transaction
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "amount": 12,
  "category": "food",
  "merchant": "Starbucks KLCC",
  "description": "Iced latte"
}

###

### Approve autosave
POST https://us-central1-thinktwice-kamihack.cloudfunctions.net/api/autosave/approve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "amount": 8,
  "nudgeId": "nudge-abc123"
}

###

### Get transactions
GET https://us-central1-thinktwice-kamihack.cloudfunctions.net/api/transactions/user123

### Create user (enxi calls this on signup)
POST https://us-central1-thinktwice-kamihack.cloudfunctions.net/api/users/setup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user123",
  "dailyBudget": 50,
  "savingsGoal": 500
}

###

### Get user profile (enxi calls this on home page load)
GET https://us-central1-thinktwice-kamihack.cloudfunctions.net/api/users/user123

###

### Update FCM token (enxi calls this after Firebase init)
PUT https://us-central1-thinktwice-kamihack.cloudfunctions.net/api/users/user123/fcm-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fcmToken": "test-fcm-token-abc123"
}

